&lt;p>Darkness was prevalent all over &lt;br>
Because it was dark everywhere outside &lt;br>
There was no light physical.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Darkness was prevalent all over &lt;br>
Because it was dark in society. &lt;br>
People were deluded, &lt;br>
They were not able to identify &lt;br>
what is right or wrong for them. &lt;br>
They are not able to choose &lt;br>
between right and wrong for others.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Relevance Of Guru</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/relevance-of-guru/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/relevance-of-guru/</guid><description>&lt;p>
